text:
Grand Central Parkway, east from 48th Street, showing the new boroughwide highway under construction. On the right is Astoria Boulevard.
View 2 shows the Parkway east from Hazen Street, and view 3 west from Hazen Street.

P. L. Sperr

October 28, 1935
Views 1,2,3
